---
title: Sweet Chilli-Glazed Tofu Poke Bowl with Radish Slaw & Spring Onion
description: We love poke bowls because they’re so versatile, you can add whatever you like! This veggie version has golden nuggets of tofu
glazed in sweet chilli sauce, along with a crunchy and fresh ponzu slaw, garlic rice and a drizzle of sriracha mayo to tie the whole
thing together.
